# Mermaid Diagrams: Bride/Groom Reindex Process

## Diagram 1: Data Flow (CSV to SearchRecord)

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["CSV File<br/>(St_Mary_1700.csv)"] -->|"Parse"| B["Freereg1CsvEntry<br/>(MongoDB document)<br/>groom_forename: John<br/>bride_forename: Jane"]
    
    B -->|"Freereg1Translator.translate()<br/>with NEW code"| C["Attributes Hash<br/>transcript_names: [<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: g, ...},<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: b, ...}<br/>]"]
    
    C -->|"SearchRecord.update_create_search_record()"| D["SearchRecord<br/>(MongoDB document)"]
    
    D -->|"Step 1-7 Transform"| E["Transformed SearchRecord<br/>transcript_names: [...]<br/>search_names: [...]<br/>search_soundex: [...]"]
    
    E -->|"Save"| F["MongoDB Database<br/>(Searchable Index Ready)"]
    
    F -->|"User queries"| G["Search Results<br/>(Displays transcript_names<br/>with groom first)"]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style B fill:#b3e5fc
    style C fill:#81d4fa
    style D fill:#4fc3f7
    style E fill:#29b6f6
    style F fill:#03a9f4
    style G fill:#039be5
```

