## Diagram 2: Reindex Lifecycle (Old vs. New Order)

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph BEFORE["BEFORE Reindex (Inconsistent)"]
        A["Old SearchRecord<br/>(Created with old translator)<br/>transcript_names: [<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: b, ...},<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: g, ...}<br/>]<br/>❌ Bride FIRST"]
        
        B["New SearchRecord<br/>(Created after code deploy)<br/>transcript_names: [<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: g, ...},<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: b, ...}<br/>]<br/>✓ Groom FIRST"]
    end
    
    subgraph TRIGGER["Reindex Trigger"]
        C["Rake Task:<br/>reprocess_batches_for_a_county[YKS]<br/>OR code change deployed"]
    end
    
    subgraph DURING["DURING Reindex (Process)"]
        D["Iterate Freereg1CsvEntry<br/>(source of truth)"]
        E["Freereg1Translator.translate()<br/>with NEW code"]
        F["SearchRecord.transform()"]
        G["Save to MongoDB"]
    end
    
    subgraph AFTER["AFTER Reindex (Consistent)"]
        H["All SearchRecords<br/>transcript_names: [<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: g, ...},<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;{role: b, ...}<br/>]<br/>✓ ALL Groom FIRST"]
    end
    
    BEFORE -->|"Initiate"| TRIGGER
    TRIGGER -->|"Start"| DURING
    DURING --> D
    D --> E
    E --> F
    F --> G
    DURING -->|"Complete"| AFTER
    
    style A fill:#ffcdd2
    style B fill:#c8e6c9
    style H fill:#c8e6c9
    style BEFORE fill:#ffebee
    style AFTER fill:#f1f8e9
```

