## Diagram 3: Translator Logic (Old vs. New)

```mermaid
graph LR
    A["Freereg1CsvEntry<br/>groom_forename: John<br/>groom_surname: Smith<br/>bride_forename: Jane<br/>bride_surname: Doe"]
    
    A -->|"OLD Code<br/>(Before Swap)"| B["Array Order:<br/>[bride, groom]<br/>[Jane Doe, John Smith]<br/>❌ Bride First"]
    
    A -->|"NEW Code<br/>(After Swap)"| C["Array Order:<br/>[groom, bride]<br/>[John Smith, Jane Doe]<br/>✓ Groom First"]
    
    B -.->|"WITHOUT Reindex<br/>Old Records Stay:<br/>Bride First"| D["Inconsistency!<br/>Old records: [b, g]<br/>New records: [g, b]"]
    
    C -->|"WITH Reindex<br/>All Records Update:<br/>Groom First"| E["Consistency!<br/>All records: [g, b]"]
    
    style A fill:#e3f2fd
    style B fill:#ffcdd2
    style C fill:#c8e6c9
    style D fill:#ffcdd2
    style E fill:#c8e6c9
```

