## Diagram 10: Rake Task Workflow

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Rake Task Start<br/>reprocess_batches_for_a_county[YKS]"]
    
    A --> B["Query MongoDB:<br/>Find all Freereg1CsvFile<br/>for county YKS"]
    
    B --> C["Loop: For each CSV file in county"]
    
    C --> D["Load CSV file metadata<br/>(file.entries.count)"]
    
    D --> E["Inner Loop: For each entry in file"]
    
    E --> F["Call Freereg1Translator<br/>with entry + file"]
    
    F --> G["Get attributes hash<br/>(new translator, groom-first)"]
    
    G --> H["searchRecord =<br/>entry.search_record"]
    
    H --> I["sr.attributes = attributes<br/>(Update with new data)"]
    
    I --> J["sr.transform()<br/>(7-step pipeline)"]
    
    J --> K["sr.save()<br/>(Write to MongoDB)"]
    
    K --> L{"More entries<br/>in file?"}
    
    L -->|"YES"| E
    L -->|"NO"| M{"More files<br/>in county?"}
    
    M -->|"YES"| C
    M -->|"NO"| N["Print summary<br/>(Total records processed)"]
    
    N --> O["✓ Task Complete"]
    
    style A fill:#e3f2fd
    style F fill:#bbdefb
    style J fill:#90caf9
    style K fill:#64b5f6
    style O fill:#4caf50
```

